Проблемы бд
некоторые значения могут повторяться - как хранить в базе

+1 Mastery: Pestilence Talent
+2 Mastery: Blood Fire Talent

в поиске: 

Mastery = (Pestilence Talent, Blood Fire Talent) 
and 
Mastery > 1

Вариант первый - завести много колонок - Mastery1 .. Mastery10
и при поиске на них все натравливать


item_example

name: Nylith's Reserve
type: Amulet
tier: Elite
slot: Neck
Requires Level 57
rarity: set
+1 Gladewalker Talents
+3 Mastery: Armageddon Talent
+24 All Stats
+15% Resist Blood
+15% Resist Poison
+24% Resist Arcarne
+15% Resist Lightning
+28% Resist Fire
+29% Resist Ice
+5% Absorb Fire
+51 Ice Spell Power
+10% Arcane Damage
+12% Resist Fear
+20% Resist Silence
-8% Enemy Resist Ice
+13% Damage: Molten Boulder
set_name: Grove Defender

INSERT INTO item (name, type, tier, rarity, armor_type, set_name, user_id, time) VALUES (NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 217341553809686528, '2024-08-16 19:21:18.021000') RETURNING id